Source: pg-cjk-parser
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), libicu-dev
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/huangjimmy/pg_cjk_parser

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-cjk-parser
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-cjk-parser
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CJK bigram full-text search parser for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_cjk_parser preserves PostgreSQL's default parser behavior while splitting
 Chinese, Japanese, and Korean text into bigram tokens in UTF-8 databases.
